00:06:05.020 --> 00:06:08.600
And let there be
another function, phi 2,

00:06:08.600 --> 00:06:10.810
such that the energy
operator acting on phi 2

00:06:10.810 --> 00:06:14.050
is also equal to E1 phi 2.

00:06:14.050 --> 00:06:16.700
