00:18:59.500 --> 00:19:04.620
normalized 2 upon
L sine of Kn x,

00:19:04.620 --> 00:19:08.790
where kn is equal to
n plus 1 pi, where

00:19:08.790 --> 00:19:11.670
n is an integer upon L.

00:19:11.670 --> 00:19:14.070
And these were chosen to
